{"tid":2160834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解３０歲揀男人一定要揀有才華、興趣、專長？","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:19:05.000Z","uid":223162,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"94c44e9650de8679119d5a85dde4312ea2812cec","tid":2160834,"uid":223162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"好明白３０歲要想成家立室埋單，搵到個男人有上進心、人生目標、事業方向，的確會大大增加左安全感。但才華、興趣、專長？<br />\n<br />\n如果一個男人同你有共興趣，當然可以增加浪漫情趣。否則，如果又唔係出色到專業搵食水平，對你地既將來有咩幫助？甚至佢平時得閒，週末都用尼發展自己興趣，少左時間陪自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以解釋下，才華、興趣、專長，係咪只係約定俗成的揀偶條件，比Ｄ港女同人晒自己男朋友幾叻幾叻？定係所謂專長只係指搵到食既一技之長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　"},{"pid":"a4702c16870af7b6257dceeb4cf1a3e374170790","tid":2160834,"uid":4740,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1481f8c91a318622bb02061bc92a3ebb70310a3","tid":2160834,"uid":38904,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQHwQpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQHwQpz.jpg&h=6d3fe937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"002bd13cb4df57b242e68f8309724fde8018267c","tid":2160834,"uid":134103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:26:19.000Z","msg":"講梗係咁講啦，唔通一嚟同你講揀男人最緊要有車有樓有錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785395e0c38972a895d0edf82d917b8f505b3fb1","tid":2160834,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4702c16870af7b6257dceeb4cf1a3e374170790","tid":2160834,"uid":4740,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTi